  {{PRINCIPLE_NUMBER}}: Sequential number for the principle
    - Type: number
    - Example: 6 or 7
    - Required: yes
    - Note: Should be next sequential number in principles array

  {{PRINCIPLE_TITLE}}: Concise title for the principle
    - Type: string
    - Example: "Security First" or "Test Coverage"
    - Required: yes

  {{SHORT_DESCRIPTION}}: Brief description shown on the principle card
    - Type: string
    - Example: "Comprehensive security scanning protects against vulnerabilities"
    - Required: yes
    - Note: Keep under 100 characters for best display

  {{FULL_DESCRIPTION}}: Detailed explanation shown in modal popup
    - Type: string (multi-line)
    - Example: "Security is integrated at every level:\n\nâ€¢ Automated dependency scanning\nâ€¢ Code security analysis\nâ€¢ Regular security updates"
    - Required: yes
