  1. Copy this principle definition to principles.config.ts principles array:
     export const principles: Principle[] = [
       // ... existing principles ...
       { principle definition here }
     ];

  2. Replace placeholders with actual values:
     - {{PRINCIPLE_NUMBER}}: Next sequential number
     - {{PRINCIPLE_TITLE}}: Clear, concise title
